name: Manipura
description: Manipura also known solar plexus chakra is the houses both the positive as well as the negative lower emotions. Positive lower emotions include ambition, daring, perseverance, strength, righteous indignation, justice and fairness. Negative lower emotions include anger,  hate, envy, greed, destructiveness, violence, worry, anxiety, fear, selfishness, aggressiveness, addiction etc. The manipura energy comes from the fire element.
